<!--
  T.A.2 — Settings sub-page strings.

  Naming: settings_<surface>_<role>; settings_cd_<thing> for icon
  content-descriptions; error_settings_<thing> for snackbar fallbacks.
  Grouped per sub-page (Common chrome / Catalog: Look and Feel /
  Personalize / Content / Audio / Root / About; then dialogs:
  Music sources / Library tabs / Sleep timer / ReplayGain pre-amp /
  Color picker / Playlist import collision / Rescan confirm / Easter
  egg / Picker labels / Multi-value separators / Search overlay).

  See also: app/src/main/res/values/strings.xml (canonical entries
  owned by other agents). All values/*.xml files merge at build time.
-->
